                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "# Portable Portrait: Alan Kay (1990)",
                                "style": {
                                    "bold": true
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "\n\n- #tags: #alan_kay #youtube #balance #harmony #stress #individual #society\n- "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "link",
                                "url": "https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=1z37SMYM3H8"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "\n- this is quite a interesting video in which alan kay shows his \"pocket he uses to travel,\n- I used to be a professional guitarist, AK: \"for me the experience of playing music ... feeling like a conduit\"\n- using a transparent bag to avoid the messiness of the office\n- What do you need for Balance (at the end)\n- ALL the stuff on the table (he calls it stress reduction stuff) to make him feel he as a balanced day even when he doesn't , in fact he uses the word stress"
                            }
